# ============================================================
# VirtusFocus Project A — .gitignore
# ============================================================
# This file controls which files Git IGNORES (does not track).
# Anything listed here will NOT appear in version history.
# ============================================================

# ----------------------------------------------------------
# RAW ATHLETE DATA (PII — personal journal entries, intake forms)
# ----------------------------------------------------------
# Weekly Reviews contain raw athlete recaps with personal
# emotional content, daily reflections, and identifiable data.
# These must never be committed to version control.
**/Weekly Reviews/

# Intake PDFs contain original athlete intake forms with
# personal information (name, school, contact, self-assessments).
# Pattern covers all athlete intake PDFs across all sport types.
Athlete Data/**/*.pdf

# ----------------------------------------------------------
# CLAUDE CODE LOCAL SETTINGS
# ----------------------------------------------------------
.claude/

# ----------------------------------------------------------
# OS AND EDITOR FILES
# ----------------------------------------------------------
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.swo
*~
~$*

# ----------------------------------------------------------
# TEMPORARY AND WORKING FILES
# ----------------------------------------------------------
*.tmp
*.bak
*.log

# ----------------------------------------------------------
# NOTE: The following ARE tracked (not ignored):
# - Athlete snapshots (processed/structured pipeline data)
# - Interpretation JSONs (pipeline output)
# - Coaching Messages and Deep Dives (pipeline output)
# - All agent prompts, instructions, and source files
# - CLAUDE.md
# - Output Comparison analysis documents
# - VF Core Program Output (historical reference)
# ----------------------------------------------------------
